node.text:
Follow @the.frenchdiver for more. It’s baby turtle season in Australia! 🐢 

“So many nests breaking out every day!”

Each year thousands of baby turtles break out of their nests and swarm the beaches of Australia. Turtle nesting season is from November to March and the baby turtles hatch from January to April peaking around February.

📽 @aleksmutated
📍 Queensland, Australia
